native": "AirPods", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/aace/49c7/1103_mini.png?m=1632981025", "stars": 75, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 1103, "parent_node_name": "apple"}, "member": {"id": 598809, "username": "saltydc", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/saltydc", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1757/4825/598809_mini.png?m=1736142529", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1757/4825/598809_normal.png?m=1736142529", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1757/4825/598809_large.png?m=1736142529", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1757/4825/598809_xlarge.png?m=1736142529", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1757/4825/598809_xxlarge.png?m=1736142529", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1757/4825/598809_xxxlarge.png?m=1736142529", "created": 1666663454, "last_modified": 1736142529, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "haiku", "last_touched": 1757832322, "title": "airpods pro 3 国行和外版有区别吗", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1158987", "created": 1757752957, "deleted": 0, "content": "硬件或者软件上，有区别吗？\n不包括血压监测那些区域问题导致的区别。", "content_rendered": "硬件或者软件上，有区别吗？<br />不包括血压监测那些区域问题导致的区别。", "last_modified": 1757823594, "replies": 31, "id": 1158987}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d6ef/5f7f/1114_large.png?m=1753446338", "name": "solana", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d6ef/5f7f/1114_normal.png?m=1753446338", "title": "Solana", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/solana", "topics": 611, "footer": "", "header": "Global State Machine", "title_alternative": "Solana", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d6ef/5f7f/1114_mini.png?m=1753446338", "stars": 562, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 1114, "parent_node_name": "crypto"}, "member": {"id": 1, "username": "Livid", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Livid", "website": "sepia.sol.build", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "Remember the bigger green", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c4ca/4238/1_mini.png?m=1757831949", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c4ca/4238/1_normal.png?m=1757831949", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c4ca/4238/1_large.png?m=1757831949", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c4ca/4238/1_xlarge.png?m=1757831949", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c4ca/4238/1_xxlarge.png?m=1757831949", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/c4ca/4238/1_xxxlarge.png?m=1757831949", "created": 1272203146, "last_modified": 1757831949, "pro": 1757833545}, "last_reply_by": "suhu", "last_touched": 1757832463, "title": "20250913 - 主题打赏功能及 Priority Fee 设置功能上线", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1159042", "created": 1757800621, "deleted": 0, "content": "如果楼主绑定了 Solana 地址，那么在 TA 发布的主题下面，就会出现这样的打赏控件：\r\n\r\n![]( https://i.v2ex.co/WipiOT2X.png)\r\n\r\n选择数量，然后点击发送，然后钱包确认即可。完全鼠标操作，不需要输入任何。\r\n\r\n手机版本的支持会在进一步测试之后加入。\r\n\r\n发送主题打赏之后，在打赏记录中可以看到是对哪个主题打赏的，接收方也会收到对应的站内提醒。\r\n\r\n![]( https://i.v2ex.co/lGvyY89K.png)\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Priority Fee 设置\r\n\r\n\r\n[settings/crypto]( https://www.v2ex.com/settings/crypto) 设置页面上加入了 Priority Fee 设置。默认值是 5000 （单位 micro-lamports ），如果加大这个数值，可能可以加快交易确认速度。\r\n\r\n![]( https://i.v2ex.co/jYRen58t.png)\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### 改进了一个打赏记录相关的问题\r\n\r\n之前在打赏完成，进行站内记录时，由于 RPC 通讯原因，某些时候记录会失败（因为没有从 RPC API 处获得交易细节）。这个步骤现在加入了多次重试机制来保证打赏记录必须在 V2EX 站内有记录。", "content_rendered": "<p>如果楼主绑定了 Solana 地址，那么在 TA 发布的主题下面，就会出现这样的打赏控件：</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.v2ex.co/WipiOT2X.png\"/></p>\n<p>选择数量，然后点击发送，然后钱包确认即可。完全鼠标操作，不需要输入任何。</p>\n<p>手机版本的支持会在进一步测试之后加入。</p>\n<p>发送主题打赏之后，在打赏记录中可以看到是对哪个主题打赏的，接收方也会收到对应的站内提醒。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.v2ex.co/lGvyY89K.png\"/></p>\n<hr/>\n<h3>Priority Fee 设置</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.v2ex.com/settings/crypto\" rel=\"nofollow\">settings/crypto</a> 设置页面上加入了 Priority Fee 设置。默认值是 5000 （单位 micro-lamports ），如果加大这个数值，可能可以加快交易确认速度。</p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.v2ex.co/jYRen58t.png\"/></p>\n<hr/>\n<h3>改进了一个打赏记录相关的问题</h3>\n<p>之前在打赏完成，进行站内记录时，由于 RPC 通讯原因，某些时候记录会失败（因为没有从 RPC API 处获得交易细节）。这个步骤现在加入了多次重试机制来保证打赏记录必须在 V2EX 站内有记录。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1757801463, "replies": 30, "id": 1159042}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/698d/51a1/111_large.png?m=1648291973", "name": "reading", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/698d/51a1/111_normal.png?m=1648291973", "title": "阅读", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/reading", "topics": 749, "footer": "", "header": "少上网，多读书", "title_alternative": "Reading", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/698d/51a1/111_mini.png?m=1648291973", "stars": 1660, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 111, "parent_node_name": "life"}, "member": {"id": 477909, "username": "xqf1126", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/xqf1126", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/66e1353ba40a1c0caa1ae22fb6f5eaf2?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/66e1353ba40a1c0caa1ae22fb6f5eaf2?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/66e1353ba40a1c0caa1ae22fb6f5eaf2?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1584719925, "last_modified": 1757818525, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "catazshadow", "last_touched": 1757833039, "title": "足矣让普通人逆袭的一本书", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1159060", "created": 1757818565, "deleted": 0, "content": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/ZUbFqtIN6fGWBIk2wW64OA", "content_rendered": "<p><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/ZUbFqtIN6fGWBIk2wW64OA\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/ZUbFqtIN6fGWBI